OL,3,CMorrisons manager says he was sacked
OL,4,Cfor tackling shoplifter
OL,6,FFormer Morrison manager Sean Egan
OL,7,Ftells Good Morning Britain his account
OL,8,Fof what happened before he was
OL,9,Fdismissed
OL,11,FA Morrisons store manager has said he
OL,12,Fwas "doing his best to protect the
OL,13,Fbusiness" when he confronted a
OL,14,Fshoplifter, but has since been sacked
OL,15,Ffrom his role.
OL,17,FSean Egan, who had worked at the
OL,18,FAldridge store in Walsall for 29
OL,19,Fyears, said he was escorting the
OL,20,Fshoplifter out of the store when the
OL,21,Fman became aggressive and spat at him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
