FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776863483
OL,3,CMorrisons manager says he was sacked
OL,4,Cfor tackling shoplifter
OL,6,F"I reacted in a way where I had to
OL,7,Fdefend myself," Mr Egan told Good
OL,8,FMorning Britain.
OL,10,F"I was put in a situation not only to
OL,11,Fdefend myself but also to ensure that
OL,12,Fcustomers and staff around me were
OL,13,Fsafe also.
OL,15,F"I had a couple of seconds in that
OL,16,Fmoment to make a decision on how this
OL,17,Fcould even pan out."
OL,19,FThe incident, he said, has had a huge
OL,20,Fimpact on his life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776863483
OL,3,CMorrisons manager says he was sacked
OL,4,Cfor tackling shoplifter
OL,6,F"I've been in a spiral of depression,
OL,7,Fgetting counselling, been medicated. I
OL,8,Fdid class Morrisons as my family and
OL,9,Fthey've been unsupportive throughout
OL,10,F... It's the only job I've ever had my
OL,11,Fentire life," he said, having started
OL,12,Fwork there aged 17.
