OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776863483
OL,3,CMorrisons manager says he was sacked
OL,4,Cfor tackling shoplifter
OL,6,F"It's been an absolute black hole of
OL,7,Fmy life so far and it's stopping me
OL,8,Ffrom progressing in what I want to
OL,9,Fdo," he said.
OL,11,FMetropolitan Police Chief Mark Rowley
OL,12,Fsaid he was "bewildered by the case".
OL,14,F"If (people) feel able to intervene
OL,15,Fand they feel they can do that safely,
OL,16,Fwe always want them to do that. We
OL,17,Fwant the public to be part of the
OL,18,Ffight against crime," he said earlier
OL,19,Fon Wednesday.
