OL,3,CMorrisons manager says he was sacked
OL,4,Cfor tackling shoplifter
OL,6,FMr Egan is also convinced that Ken
OL,7,FMorrison, the late chairman of the
OL,8,Fsupermarket and son of founder William
OL,9,FMorrison, would've been proud of how
OL,10,Fhe responded on that day.
OL,12,F"He would've said 'well done son'," Mr
OL,13,FEgan said.
OL,15,F'He was out to cause trouble'
OL,17,FMr Egan described in detail his
OL,18,Faccount of what happen at the shop in
OL,19,FAldridge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
