OL,3,CMorrisons manager says he was sacked
OL,4,Cfor tackling shoplifter
OL,6,F"The shoplifter was selecting bottles
OL,7,Fof spirits in the booze aisle ... I
OL,8,Fasked for the products back as part of
OL,9,Fout policy, he said no... There was no
OL,10,Fsecurity guard on duty at the time and
OL,11,FI had to escort him out," he said.
OL,13,FHe said the shoplifter put a hand into
OL,14,Fhis bag - which contained the alcohol
OL,15,Fand other unknown items - so he put
OL,16,Fhis arm out and happened to catch the
OL,17,Fman by the chest.
OL,19,F"I grabbed him arm to stop him going
OL,20,Fin the bag... What happened then was
OL,21,Fan altercation in the self-scan area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776863483
OL,3,CMorrisons manager says he was sacked
OL,4,Cfor tackling shoplifter
OL,6,F"I was in the situation where this guy
OL,7,Fwas strong as a bear ... Another
OL,8,Fmanager came to restrain him ... but
OL,9,Fhe was still swinging."
OL,11,FMr Egan said that he and a colleague
OL,12,Fgot the shoplifter out of the store
OL,13,Fand flagged down local police who
OL,14,Fapprehended him.
OL,16,F"He was aggressive and he was out to
OL,17,Fcause trouble," he said.
OL,19,FThe former Morrisons worker has said
OL,20,Fthat since being dismissed he is still
OL,21,Flooking for work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
