OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776863483
OL,3,CMorrisons manager says he was sacked
OL,4,Cfor tackling shoplifter
OL,6,F"But would I work in a supermarket
OL,7,Fagain? It's left a sour taste," he
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,FMorrisons told Good Morning Britain:
OL,11,F"While we cannot comment on individual
OL,12,Fcases, we're confident this matter was
OL,13,Finvestigated thoroughly and that the
OL,14,Fcorrect process was followed. The
OL,15,Fsubsequent reporting does not reflect
OL,16,Fthe full facts of the situation. We're
OL,17,Fcontinuing to take wide-ranging action
OL,18,Fto address the threat of shoplifting
OL,19,For violence in our stores."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
